phrases: HALF
TS
As of this moment, 18 plants, or 95 of the terrestrial plant corals have been reactivated
and are under attack by Secrets.
At this rate, even if we deploy our full strength,
we will not be able to prevent Scub Bursts at most of the Plants.
Therefore, we are commencing Operation Polaris.
Papa...
We are going to utilize the powerful radiation released by the Quartz we have secured so far
to gather the Secrets spread throughout the world in one place.
By putting all the Quartz on a descending orbit,
we are going to lure away the Secrets over a period of 36 hours,
and eventually crash the capsule at the North Pole.
As the North Pole is uninhabited, we will allow the confluence explosion to occur, thus...
The Secrets will be destroyed.
Cannot you at least split them up into multiple groups?
It will not be as effective if we lower the explosion's yield.
We just cannot lower our firepower.
Anyway, could I ask you to do me a favor?
What is it?
Seeing that you are stranded in South America anyway,
could you buy me some coffee beans?
I cannot drink this crap.
It tastes like Starbucks.
Sorry for calling before you leave.
Ao, do you have the pills with you?
You should sleep some, or you will not last long.
Yeah.
You still cannot get it off your mind?
I have been fighting Secrets for all this time.
But, somehow, it feels different this time.
Do you want to go back to Iwato Island then?
Amongst the sudden crisis of impending Scub Bursts from all around the world,
Christophe Blanc, the CEO of the Swiss company, Generation Blue,
has suggested the launch of Operation Polaris.
Numerous countries, including the US, have expressed their full support for the operation.
Generation Bleu hid the existence of this Quartz material from the rest of the world!
Who is going to take the responsibility for that?
The Japanese government reinforced its position that Secrets are the saviors of mankind,
and asked its citizens to not be misled by irresponsible announcements and stay cal
Quite a few countries are taking part in the operation, right?
Are we going to panic and rally under their flags?
Are you telling me to back the winning horse?
If this operation succeeds, we will finally be freed from the threat of Scub Bursts,
which has loomed over us since the dawn of history.
I am Maruyama from the VOM.
What are the chances of success for Generation Bleu's operation?
According to our estimations, if the Scub Bursts were to occur around the world,
the immediate effects would claim at least 60 million lives,
and the environmental aftereffects would endanger another 300 million.
We have no choice but to put our trust in them.
I did not expect Blanc to make such a move.
You could have at least notified the Big Blue World.
Does Blanc think the Quartz are his private property?
I am very sorry.
He does not seem to comprehend that Generation Blue is an organization created for the Quartz.
What does that mean?
Is that Ao?
Do not be afraid!
I will do something about it!
Naru?!
Naru...
Why?
Prepare the Small Arc for launch.
Where is Ao and the other kids?
They are on standby at the starting point.
So much Quartz...
You must have suppressed their radiation so that we could not sense them.
Georg?
Please ignore that.
Shall we do this, then?
Five seconds left.
Four.
Three.
Two.
One.
Hey, that was way too quick!
Let Operation Polaris begin.
What is that?
What is that light?
It is the capsule that was launched from the Poseidon.
The Quartz are stacked up in that.
Got him!
It ran away?
Why did the Secret do that?
Damn you, Generation Bleu!
They are here!
They are enamored...
The is one hell of a Quartz pheromone!
Keep herding the Secrets.
However, stay alert and do not let them get close to the capsule.
Do not try to destroy them.
Roger!
Hey, mister, this way!
Ao, we are going!
Huh?
Okay!
Secrets...
So you are not our enemies?
But we have been fighting you all this time.
Where...
You smell nice.
I should not have asked you!
I would kill for a shower...
Good morning.
You have slept soundly.
I slept?
Oh, I see...
Fleur even drew on your willy, but you would not wake up.
I did not!
You are good to go.
See you guys at the next supply point.
Thanks.
What is the American casualty count?
Seven units were hit and destroyed,
but no one has died so far.
All right!
The heroes are back!
Wow...
Alex and his engineering team brought all that from the HQ.
And...
The Allied Forces are fighting alongside us.
It feels like we are nearing the last episode!
I have got a bad feeling about that.
There is a Secret at the VesterAlen Plant?
Is not that Maeve and Chloe's place?
What?
It is their hometown.
Their parents work at the Plant, so they moved there.
That is why Chloe's gotten used to trapar since she was little.
The Secret from Norway is headed for the Quartz too.
Cut the pointless chatter.
Sure...
If their hometown is like that, then Iwato Island is...
Must suck for you to be stuck here.
But will this operation whatever really work out?
Of course.
Our army is fully cooperating as well.
Unfortunately, you are all going down.
Our only purpose is to erase alien materials from this space.
By doing this, we can eliminate large amounts of such materials.
I do not give a single damn about that.
I am afraid they are quite serious about that.
I was born from the Scub Coral.
So were you.
You are a child of the Scub, Ao.
I have become one with it, too.
Protect the Scub, Ao...
But Mom...
She said that the Scub is the enemy.
Decide for yourself.
Ao...
Ao!
I am sorry!
What are you talking about?!
Team Goldilocks are in trouble!
Twelve minutes ago, Soviet ballistic missiles were launched.
But are not they a part of Polaris?
But the missiles are on a course of collision with the capsule.
They claim their missile control system is under cyberattack.
Goldilocks and Harlequin have been on standby in case something like this happened.
I am out of ammo.
I will not let you!
The Quartz are very important to us!
We are going to protect it!
The missiles' shockwaves have pushed the capsule off its trajectory.
At this rate, it will crash south from the North Polein North Europe.
The IFOs must carry it to the North Pole.
That is crazy!
We are going to carry it until Alleluia and Kyrie run out of fuel.
Then we are leaving it to Nirvash's Third Engine.
The Third Engine uses trapar inside the atmosphere.
Which means you have the most fuel out of all of us.
Elena?
After Alleluia and Kyrie have launched,
the Triton will proceed to its final position.
Chief?
I know it is risky...
What about team Goldilocks?
The newbie's there?
You seriously have time to worry about us?
We know you are happy about it.
But I am not!
Ao, we are counting on you to protect our hometown.
We have caught up.
Let us go, Alleluia!
Caught it.
Geez
There should have been enough distance!
They must have gotten enthusiastic when the capsule lost its altitude.
Elena, please!
Alrighty!
Hey!
That is cheating!
Elena!
Elena!
Georg!
The status on Kyrie!
There is some damage, but it can still fly.
The pilot's fine as well.
Elena, we are sending the Allied Forces to pick you up, so retreat for now.
Alleluia's restrictor has been released.
Fleur, do you want to start the Third Engine?
If I do not do it now, when will I?
But until now it would not
I am doing it!
Booting Third Engine...
Activate!
No way!
It disconnected!
Why...
Why will not it start?!
This is President Christophe Blanc.
The plan has changed.
Although we have yet to reach the destination,
we are going to commence the confluence explosion.
Papa...?
Fleur!
Throw away the Quartz and get as far away from it as possible.
This is an order.
Our calculations tell us that if we have it detonate now, most of the Secrets would be destroyed.
We will deploy team Harlequin to deal with the rest.
What about potential casualties?
A part of the Scandinavian Peninsula will be erased.
We have just issued an evacuation order.
Gazelle...
It is decided.
Wait, what?!
What happened?
The catapult is opening on its own!
What?!
Ao, are you acting on your own again?!
Nirvash is the only one with an operational Third Engine!
That is why I have to go and do it!
Ao!
Dispatch authorized.
Chief?!
But you must come back.
You are not Eureka.
Yessir!
Dammit...
The manipulator will not last much longer.
Something is closing in?
Fleur, I will do it!
Ao?
But...
Pick up Elena and return to the Triton!
Alleluia's damaged and I have got the advantage!
Okay.
You must come back!
Okay...
We are going, Nirvash!
Alleluia left the capsule and Nirvash started accelerating.
Ao, be careful!
The Secrets are catching up!
You are closing in on the VesterAlen Plant!
I know!
Retrieve Kyrie and Alleluia.
We are going provide cover for Nirvash.
We are now off-shore.
However, we cannot gain distance on the Secrets.
The chances of you escaping the confluence explosion alive is 3 at this point.
Ten years ago, Mom disappeared somewhere with the Quartz.
I do not know where Mom came from.
But if her blood is in my veins...
If we share the same blood...
Then I must be able to fly too.
Fly with me, Quartz!
This light...
What is this?!
Ao, what is going on?!
What is this?
What is going on?!
Answer me, Nirvash!
A weapon?
Is this a weapon?
If it is a weapon, then save the world with it!
We cannot confirm any remaining Secrets.
Good job, Ao, despite it not being a part of the plan.
Can you explain to us about that weapon?
I cannot.
What is that?
A North Pole light.
It is a mysterious light phenomenon often seen around here.
No, that light is...
It is the Vester Shuttle's supply point.
Vester?
The Plant?
And the Coral Plant?
There is never been one here.
Well...
What about team Goldilocks?
Are Chloe and the other two all right?
Chloe?
I will ask you again, Ao.
What is this team Goldilocks you are talking about?
They are an IFO team just like us.
Generation Bleu has only two IFO teams: Pied Piper and Harlequin.
Pied Piper handles terrestrial affairs while Harlequin is stationed in space.
But...
But they were here!
Why will not you remember them?
Why does not anyone...
No matter how hard you look, there is nothing.
No one's lived here for centuries.
No.
Chloe said she was...
I went through the medical checkup data.
Chloe McCaffrey, Maeve McCaffrey, and Maggie Kwan.
There is no such personnel.
There never have been.
Anyway, just take a rest.
You must be tired.
What have I done, Mom?
To be continued.
Next time on Eureka Seven AO.
The world should have been saved by the light Nirvash unleashed.
But as Ao is the only one who knows the truth, he must shoulder the heavy price all alone.
The boy's salvation moves the gears in the machine.
Eureka Seven AO, episode 17: La Vie en Rose.
Listen to the voices of the children of the stars.
Guardian's Hammer
